item.description:
Taylor Swift - The Eras Tour Extended 2023 2160p AMZN WEB-DL H265 HDR10 [HEVC + AAC]

After a month of deciding if I should share what I had been working on, I have decided to share that I have upscaled / remapped the eras tour extended film souced from AMZN from SDR into HDR10, and organized them into their individual eras.

Unfortunately, I was only able to do the individual songs one by one and not the full thing all at once, so i skipped the talking segments between the songs, but kept most of the transitions between the eras.

I know this isnt an official HDR release so there may be flaws but I hope it helps anyone out there looking to watch it in HDR10 instead of the Dolby Vision version shared a few days ago.

Extra: I'm not sure what or how it happened with my encoding software, but the overall bitrate of the film has increased from 21.2Mb/s to around 36-37Mb/s, and I didnt encode it with the Dolby Atmos EA3 audio.
